                <h1>Planning and Administration Department</h1>
                
                    <div class="pageDescription"><p>The Planning and Administration Department is the Ministry’s administration and operations department with responsibility for pay and personnel policy, coordination of work on the budget both in the justice sector and internally. The department has also overall responsibility for IT in the justice sector, as well as for research and organization analyses in the Ministry.</p>
<p>The department is divided into&nbsp;four sections.</p></div>        
                
